'''愛爾蘭流浪者'''（[[爱尔兰语|爱尔兰语]]：an lucht siúil）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mayock |first1=Breda |title=The Role of Hair in Traveller Culture |url=https://educationmatters.ie/the-role-of-hair-in-traveller-culture/ |accessdate=15 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816095210/https://educationmatters.ie/the-role-of-hair-in-traveller-culture/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一个游牧民族，他们主要讲[[英语|英语]]，但许多人也讲[[雪爾塔語|雪爾塔語]]。在宗教上，大多数愛爾蘭流浪者信奉[[天主教|天主教]]。

虽然他们经常被称为[[罗姆人|罗姆人]]，但愛爾蘭流浪者与罗姆人在基因上并无亲缘关系<ref name="Griffin">{{cite book|last=Griffin|first=Rosarii |year=2014|title=Education in Indigenous, Nomadic and Travelling Communities|language=en |location=|publisher=A&C Black|isbn=9781472511195|page=50|url=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thejournal.ie/traveller-community-study-rcsi-3231070-Feb2017/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |archive-date=2020-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203133437/https://www.thejournal.ie/traveller-community-study-rcsi-3231070-Feb2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基因分析表明，愛爾蘭流浪者很可能是在17世纪[[克伦威尔征服爱尔兰|克伦威尔征服爱尔兰]]期间从定居的爱尔兰人中分化而来。数百年的分离导致愛爾蘭流浪者在基因上与定居的[[爱尔兰人|爱尔兰人]]有所区别<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Gilbert|first1=Edmund|last2=Carmi|first2=Shai|last3=Ennis|first3=Sean|last4=Wilson|first4=James F.|last5=Cavalleri|first5=Gianpiero L.|date=2017-02-16|title=Genomic insights into the population structure and history of the Irish Travellers|journal=Scientific Reports|language=en|volume=7|issue=1|page=42187|doi=10.1038/srep42187|pmid=28181990|pmc=5299991|issn=2045-2322}}</ref>，愛爾蘭流浪者权益组织长期以来一直向爱尔兰政府要求承認愛爾蘭流浪者為獨立的民族，2017年，愛爾蘭政府正式承認愛爾蘭流浪者是一個獨立的民族<ref>{{cite news | newspaper=The Independent | date=March 1, 2017 | title=Taoiseach formally recognises ethnic status | url=http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/politics/hundreds-of-irish-travellers-left-outside-leinster-house-as-taoiseach-formally-recognises-ethnic-status-35494069.html | accessdate=2020-09-16 | archive-date=2017-03-30 | archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/10702/20170330185000/http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/politics/hundreds-of-irish-travellers-left-outside-leinster-house-as-taoiseach-formally-recognises-ethnic-status-35494069.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

愛爾蘭流浪者大多生活在爱尔兰，以及[[英国|英国]]、美国和[[加拿大|加拿大]]的大型社区中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.paveepoint.ie/pav_faq_a.html|title=Questioning Gypsy|website=paveepoint.ie|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001000038/http://www.paveepoint.ie/pav_faq_a.html|archivedate=1 October 2011}}</ref>。截至2016年，爱尔兰境内有32302名愛爾蘭流浪者。他们占爱尔兰共和国总人口的0.7%<ref>{{Cite web|title=Irish Travellers - Demographics - CSO - Central Statistics Office|url=https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-cp8iter/p8iter/p8itd/#:~:text=The%20total%20number%20of%20usually,on%20the%20usually%20resident%20population.|access-date=2020-08-25|website=www.cso.ie|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809203703/https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-cp8iter/p8iter/p8itd/#:~:text=The%20total%20number%20of%20usually,on%20the%20usually%20resident%20population.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

